ult-owner-louis-vuitton-lvmh-net-worth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBernard%20Arnault%3C%2Fa%3E's%20family%2C%20who%20had%20amassed%20a%20similar-sized%20fortune%20to%20Buffett%20by%20investing%20in%20luxury%20fashion%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20to%20Point72%20CEO%20Steve%20Cohen%20and%20the%20late%20Renaissance%20Technologies%20founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjim-simons-dead-obituary-founder-renaissance-technologies-hedge-fund-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJim%20Simons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20became%20billionaires%20by%20actively%20trading%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssia%20said%20it%20became%20clear%20to%20him%20there%20wasn't%20only%20one%20way%20to%20invest%20successfully%2C%20and%20people%20needed%20to%20pick%20the%20approach%20that%20works%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20eToro%20enables%20that%20by%20letting%20users%20learn%20from%20each%20other%2C%20and%20even%20copy%20their%20peers'%20portfolios%20if%20they%20choose%20to%20share%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c3a29b2-68c0-4724-bd4f-52df0c5065cf%5C%22%3E'Everyone%20deserves%20a%20quant'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EeToro%20has%20rolled%20out%20several%20user-built%2C%20AI-powered%20applications%20as%20it%20prepares%20to%20launch%20an%20app%20store-like%20marketplace%20for%20those%20types%20of%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20tool%20lets%20users%20discuss%20their%20portfolios%20with%20AI%20versions%20of%20investing%20%26quot%3Btitans%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20Buffett%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-stock-market-inflation-recession-peter-lynch-magellan-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPeter%20Lynch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20helping%20any%20kind%20of%20investor%20improve%20their%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20mines%20a%20user's%20trades%20for%20insights%20such%20as%20their%20most%20productive%20period%20of%20the%20day%2C%20which%20could%20help%20them%20fine-tune%20their%20s