%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-talk-dirty-sex-erotic-star-tips-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etalking%20about%20sex%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20them%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20helped%20me%20convey%20my%20messages%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20contraception%20and%20the%20idea%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funbound-bloomi-founders-talk-social-media-ad-censorship-sex-health-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esexual%20wellness%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20part%20of%20overall%20health.%20But%20it%20didn't%20make%20things%20less%20awkward.%20Talking%20with%20my%20son%20was%20particularly%20tricky.%20He%20was%20even%20more%20uncomfortable%20than%20my%20daughters.%20Despite%20my%20openness%2C%20he%20never%20brought%20the%20topic%20up%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20I%20wasn't%20going%20to%20force%20him%20to%20talk%20about%20sex%2C%20but%20I%20was%20going%20to%20ask%20him%20to%20listen.%20There%20were%20some%20things%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20share%20with%20him%2C%20including%20the%20importance%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Ftypes-of-emergency-contraception-how-to-choose%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemergency%20contraception%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20ways%20that%20women's%20sexual%20pleasure%20was%20different%20from%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22314f2a96-ecdf-48bb-9aad-b9ad9c9223b2%5C%22%3EMy%20son%20thought%20it%20was%20funny%20that%20I%20gave%20him%20emergency%20contraceptives%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20emphasize%20to%20my%20son%20that%20contraception%20isn't%20only%20a%20woman's%20responsibility.%20We%20discussed%20the%20importance%20of%20condoms%2C%20but%20also%20that%20condoms%20fail%2010%25%20to%2015%25%20of%20the%20time.%20In%20those%20cases%2C%20I%20told%20him%2C%20it%20made%20sense%20for%20him%20to%20have%20emergency%20contraception%20on%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221652%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samantha%20Miller%20and%20her%20family%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b076c1ccda166eed3d1d35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221164%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(second%20from%20left)%20and%20her%20family%20are%20comfortable%20talking%20about%20sex.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Samantha%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20went%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-a-college-degree-worth-it-majors-completion-living-costs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoff%20to%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20to%20send%20him%20with%20emergency%20contraception%2C%20just%20in%20case.%20The%20product%20will%20last%20a%20few%20years%2C%20so%20you%20only%20have%20to%20buy%20it%20once.%20If%20there's%20ever%20a%20question%20about%20whether%20the%20sex%20was%20safe%20%E2%80%94%20like%20not%20being%20able%20to%20find%20the%20condom%20after%20intercourse%20%E2%80%94%20I%20wanted%20him%20to%20have%20the%20pill%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20funny%20and%20got%20a%20kick%20out%20of%20telling%20his%20friends%20that%20he%20had%20the%20emergency%20contraception.%20I%20told%20him%20that%20being%20responsible%20in%20this%20way%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20impress%20the%20ladies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20one%20of%20his%20friends%20unintentionally%20got%20a%20woman%20pregnant%20and%20was%20thrust%20into%20fatherhood%20before%20he%20planned.%20Seeing%20what%20his%20friend%20has%20gone%20through%20has%20been%20a%20crash%20course%20in%20the%20importance%20of%20taking%20accountability%20for%20contraception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5eb4627-d08c-4888-b334-b70b9a050cc7%5C%22%3EI%20taught%20my%20son%20to%20think%20about%20his%20partner's%20pleasure%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20topic%20that%20made%20my%20son%20cringe%20the%20most%20was%20discussing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-penetrative-sex-more-pleasurable-for-women-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efemale%20pleasure%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20topic%20didn't%20bother%20me%20at%20all%3B%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20wisdom%20to%20share.%20But%20I%20kept%20the%20conversation%20pretty%20high-level%20because%20he%20was%20uncomfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20plant%20the%20seed%20that%20female%20pleasure%20is%20different%20from%20what%20my%20son%20experiences%20as%20a%20male.%20It's%20more%20complex%2C%20requires%20more%20explanation%2C%20and%20doesn't%20happen%20reliably%20with%20intercourse%20the%20way%20male%20pleasure%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20need%20to%20say%20much%3B%20we%20didn't%20talk%20about%20anatomy.%20But%20I%20emphasized%20that%20female%20pleasure%20is%20important%2C%20and%20something%20my%20son%20needs%20to%20check%20in%20with%20his%20partners%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22105efcc0-02bd-4fb0-831c-7d7aad3c65f9%5C%22%3EI%20wish%20the%20adults%20in%20my%20life%20had%20talked%20more%20candidly%20about%20sex%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20talked%20with%20the%20adults%20in%20my%20life%20about%20sex.%20Honestly%2C%20things%20would%20have%20gone%20better%20for%20me%20if%20I%20had.%20Talking%20with%20older%20adults%20can%20help%20young%20people%20develop%20a%20maturity%20around%20sex%2C%20and%20I%20wish%20I'd%20had%20that%20guidance%20when%20I%20was%20younger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20safe%2C%20pleasurable%20sex%20life%20is%20part%20of%20overall%20health.%20The%20more%20we%20can%20talk%20about%20that%2C%20the%20more%20empowered%20we'll%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20my%20kids%20are%20adults%20now%2C%20I%20still%20talk%20with%20all%20of%20them%20about%20sex.%20While%20it%20isn't%20always%20the%20most%20comfortable%2C%20I'm%20glad%20we%20can%20have%20those%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-sent-son-to-college-with-emergency-contraception-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773313621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b0766b82b35e2c04dd74be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-sent-son-to-college-with-emergency-contraception-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20work%20in%20sex%20education%2C%20so%20I'm%20comfortable%20talking%20about%20sex%20with%20most%20people%2C%20even%20my%20children.%20But%20my%20son%20didn't%20love%20having%20these%20talks%20with%20me.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-sent-son-to-college-with-emergency-contraception-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Naga%20Chaitanya%20flaunts%20six-pack%20look%20for%20%E2%80%98Vrusha%20Karma%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773313589000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129504630%2Cimgsize-64210.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftelugu%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fnaga-chaitanyas-beast-mode-transformation-is-unmissable-actor-flaunts-six-pack-look-for-vrusha-karma%2Farticleshow%2F129504630.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129504630.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENaga%20Chaitanya%20has%20unveiled%20a%20dramatic%20six-pack%20transformation%20for%20his%20upcoming%20adventure%20thriller%2C%20'Vrusha%20Karma.'%20The%20actor%20shared%20a%20gym%20photo%20as%20his%20character%20Arjun%2C%20showcasing%20a%20muscular%20physique%20and%20rugged%20beard.%20This%20intense%20physical%20makeover%20for%20the%20treasure%20hunter%20role%20has%20generated%20significant%20excitement%20among%20fa