first-acquisition-and-the-great-legal-tech-rollup-continues-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMelia%20was%20first%20to%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Legora%20used%20its%20new%20%24550%20million%20funding%20round%20to%20secure%20its%20first%20acquisition%2C%20Canadian%20legal-tech%20startup%20Walter.%20(I'm%20not%20sure%20why%20legal%20tech%20loves%20using%20first%20names%20for%20their%20companies.%20I'll%20check%20with%20Melia%20on%20that%20one.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20to%20be%20outdone%2C%20Harvey%20is%20partnering%20with%20The%20LegalTech%20Fund%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvey-legaltech-fund-legal-tech-startups-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20start%20investing%20in%20young%20legal-tech%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20times%2C%20as%20Melia%20has%20previously%20reported.%20Legal-tech%20giants%20looking%20to%20add%20more%20features%20and%20specialities%20to%20their%20products%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flegal-tech-mergers-acquisitions-consolidation-clio-harvey-filevine-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eare%20hunting%20for%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegora%20and%20Harvey's%20biggest%20fight%20might%20not%20ultimately%20be%20with%20each%20other.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20still%20traditional%20legal%20players%20like%20Thomson%20Reuters%20and%20RELX.%20And%20while%20they've%20certainly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-cowork-legal-plugin-publishing-stocks-legalzoom-thomson-reuters-relx-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaken%20some%20bumps%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20still%20hold%20an%20incredible%20amount%20of%20proprietary%20data%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-legal-ai-tool-plugin-competition-lexisnexis-thomson-reuters-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20gives%20them%20a%20stro