0lethal%20hand%20grenade%20since%20Vietnam%20for%20full%20material%20release.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20M111%20will%20replace%20the%20asbestos-made%20MK3A2%20blast%20grenade.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Army%2C%20the%20new%20grenade%20is%20safer%20for%20close-quarters%20combat%20indoors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20nearly%20six%20decades%2C%20the%20US%20Army%20is%20getting%20a%20new%20lethal%20hand%20grenade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20cleared%20the%20new%20M111%20Offensive%20Hand%20Grenade%20for%20full%20production%20this%20week.%20The%20new%20blast%20overpressure%20grenade%20is%20replacing%20the%20now-obsolete%20MK3A2%20grenades%2C%20which%20were%20first%20adopted%20by%20the%20military%20in%201968%2C%20around%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20M67%20fragmentation%20grenade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Capabilities%20Program%20Executive%20Ammunition%20and%20Energetics%2C%20together%20with%20US%20Army%20Combat%20Capabilities%20Development%20Command%20Armaments%20Center%20at%20Picatinny%20Arsenal%2C%20developed%20the%20new%20hand%20grenade%2C%20the%20first%20for%20the%20Army%20since%20Vietnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20M111%20is%20made%20of%20plastic%20that%20is%20consumed%20during%20detonation.%20The%20older%20MK3A2%20blast%2Fconcussion%20grenades%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20were%20made%20from%20asbestos%2C%20a%20carcinogenic%20substance%20that%20forced%20the%20service%20to%20put%20restrictions%20on%20the%20use%20of%20these%20grenades.%20The%20old%20M67%20grenades%20are%20still%20in%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20value%20of%20having%20a%20blast%20overpressure%20grenade%20is%20that%20it%20decreases%20the%20risk%20of%20unintentional%20fratricide%2C%20the%20accidental%20killing%20of%20one's%20own%20troops%20at%20war%2C%20during%20close-quarters%20combat%2C%20but%20the%20limitations%20on%20the%20use%20of%20the%20MK3A2%20meant%20soldiers%20only%20had%20the%20fragmentation%20M67%20available%20to%20them%20in%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20M67%20grenade%20propels%20metal%20fragments%20outward%20in%20all%20directions%20when%20it%20explodes.%20In%20tight%20indoor%20spaces%20like%20rooms%20or%20hallways%2C%20those%20fragments%20can%20bounce%20off%20walls%20or%20be%20blocked%20by%20furniture%2C%20reducing%20effectiveness%20and%20potentially%20hurting%20friendly%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20M111%20grenade%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20MK3A2%2C%20works%20differently%2C%20instead%20producing%20a%20powerful%20blast%20and%20pressure%20wave%20less%20likely%20to%20be%20stopped%20by%20walls%20or%20obstacles%2C%20making%20it%20more%20effective%20inside%20buildings%20and%20other%20confined%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20key%20lessons%20learned%20from%20the%20door-to-door%20urban%20fighting%20in%20Iraq%20was%20the%20M67%20grenade%20wasn't%20always%20the%20right%20tool%20for%20the%20job.%20The%20risk%20of%20fratricide%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20wall%20was%20too%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Col.%20Vince%20Morris%2C%20the%20Army%20project%20manager%20for%20close%20combat%20systems%2C%20in%20a%20service%20press%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20blast%20overpressure%20instead%2C%20%26quot%3Bcan%20clear%20a%20room%20of%20enemy%20combatants%20quickly%20leaving%20nowhere%20to%20hide%20while%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20friendly%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoldiers%20can%20still%20use%20the%20M67%20fragmentation%20hand%20grenade%20in%20open%20terrain%2C%20the%20statement%20said%2C%20but%20should%20rely%20on%20the%20newer%20version%20for%20%26quot%3Benclosed%20and%20restricted%20terrain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlast%20overpressure%20weapons%20can%20be%20harmful%20for%20troops%20using%20them%2C%20and%20the%20US%20military%20has%20been%20grappling%20with%20the%20effects%20of%20these%20systems.%20Service%20members%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20their%20continuous%20work%20with%20artillery%2C%20breaching%20charges%2C%20and%20other%20heavy%20weaponry%2C%20have%20suffered%20traumatic%20brain%20injuries%2C%20which%20can%20come%20with%20debilitating%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%2C%20along%20with%20other%20services%2C%20has%20sought%20to%20mitigate%20these%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-us-army-is-getting-a-new-hand-grenade-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773310321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b1c81ea96e437d6eb8287f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-us-army-is-getting-a-new-hand-grenade-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Army%20has%20approved%20the%20M111%20hand%20grenade%2C%20the%20first%20new%20lethal%20hand%20grenade%20since%20Vietnam%2C%20to%20replace%20the%20MK3A2%20for%20indoor%20combat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbaker%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-us-army-is-getting-a-new-hand-grenade-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UFC%20Fighters%20to%20Train%20FBI%20Agents%20in%20%E2%80%98Historic%20Seminar%E2%80%99%20This%20Week%3A%20We%E2%80%99ll%20%E2%80%98Be%20Even%20Better%20Prepared%20to%20Protect%20the%20American%20People%2C%E2%80%99%20Kash%20Patel%20Says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773310291000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236685597%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22UFC%20fighters%20will%20head%20to%20Quantico%2C%20Va.%20this%20week%20to%20train%20FBI%20agents%20and%20students%20in%20what%20FBI%20director%20Kash%20Patel%20is%20calling%20a%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%20seminar.%E2%80%9D%20According%20to%20a%20press%20release%20from%20UFC%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20mixed%20martial%20arts%20promotion%20company%20has%20partnered%20with%20the%20FBI%20for%20a%20training%20course%20taking%20place