usinessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20entering%20unfamiliar%20territory%20with%20a%20%24599%20MacBook%2C%20and%20competitors%20are%20noticing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20giant%20is%20known%20for%20high%20price%20tags%20on%20pretty%20much%20all%20of%20its%20gadgets%2C%20but%20every%20once%20and%20while%20it%20offers%20an%20affordable%20option%20for%20those%20who%20want%20a%20lower%20price%20point.%20Such%20is%20the%20case%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmacbook-neo-apple-lower-cost-affordable-specs-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20MacBook%20Neo%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20revealed%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20at%20%24599%2C%20the%20MacBook%20Neo%20sells%20for%20%24500%20less%20than%20an%20entry-level%20MacBook%20Air.%20It%20costs%20less%20than%20an%20iPhone%2017%2C%20and%20it%20runs%20on%20an%20A18%20Pro%20chip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drop%20is%20making%20waves%20in%20the%20laptop%20business%20as%20Apple%20enters%20a%20new%20price%20bracket.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fblack-friday%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETaiwanese%20PC%20maker%20Asus%3C%2Fa%3E%20fielded%20questions%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20affordable%20MacBook%20Neo%20during%20its%20earnings%20call%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20Apple's%20historically%20very%20premium%20pricing%2C%20launching%20such%20an%20affordable%20product%20is%20certainly%20a%20shock%20to%20the%20entire%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Asus%20financial%20chief%20Nick%20Wu%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%20transcript%20translated%20to%20English%20that%20was%20published%20by%20Seeking%20Alpha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20said%20Asus%20observed%20%26quot%3Blimitations%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20MacBook%20Neo%2C%20such%20as%20its%208%20GB%20of%20memory%2C%20which%20may%20limit%20certain%20applications.%20He%20said%20the%20device%20seems%20to%20be%20more%20focused%20on%20content%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20differs%20somewhat%20from%20mainstream%20notebook%20usage%20scenarios%2C%26quot%3B%20Wu%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Neo%20feels%20more%20like%20a%20tablet%2C%20because%20tablets%20are%20mostly%20for%20content%20consumption.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20comparison%2C%20the%20lowest-memory%20laptop%20available%20on%20the%20Asus%20website%20on%20Wednesday%20was%20the%20ZenBook%2014%20with%2016%20GB%20of%20memory.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20positioned%20the%20new%20laptop%20as%20an%20accessible%20product%20that%20aims%20to%20put%20the%20MacBook%20in%20more%20people's%20hands%20around%20the%20world.%20The%20introduction%20of%20a%20lower-cost%20laptop%20came%20alongside%20a%20round%20of%20price%20increases%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-macbook-air-pro-m5-prices-increase-memory-shortage-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehigher-end%20MacBooks%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Apple%20has%20officially%20entered%20a%20new%2C%20lower%20price%20lane%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20rivals%20are%20bound%20to%20take%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWu%20said%20all%20PC%20vendors%20are%20taking%20this%20%26quot%3Bvery%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20expects%20rivals%20to%20launch%20their%20own%20products%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20MacBook%20Neo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20final%20market%20competition%20outcome%20is%20hard%20to%20predict%2C%26quot%3B%20Wu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-599-macbook-neo-shock-to-affordable-laptop-market-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773309301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b17182a96e437d6eb81c87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-599-macbook-neo-shock-to-affordable-laptop-market-202