Even%20after%20finishing%20her%20degree%2C%20Brown%20struggled%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20for%20years%20as%20she%20paved%20her%20way%20into%20the%20beauty%20industry%20as%20a%20young%20makeup%20artist.%20It%20took%20her%20years%20to%20build%20a%20reputation%20and%20eventually%20her%20own%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20experienced%20both%20uncertainty%20and%20success%2C%20Brown%20has%20simple%20advice%20for%20recent%20grads%20facing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-hired-job-search-white-collar-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emurky%20job%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BDon't%20worry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20supposed%20to%20know%20now%2C%20and%20you%20got%20to%20try%20some%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20that%20if%20you're%20in%20a%20career%20lull%20or%20unsure%20of%20your%20next%20move%2C%20the%20first%20step%20is%20recognizing%20that%20it's%20normal.%20Early%20on%2C%20she%20said%2C%20you%20really%20only%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20two%20things%3A%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20pay%20your%20rent%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20staying%20open%20to%20new%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20just%20got%20to%20try%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20internships%20are%20great.%20Temporary%20positions%20are%20great.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296860052-b8b0-4666-9e5f-43f9f8757812%5C%22%3EFollow%20your%20interests%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20memoir%2C%20%26quot%3BStill%20Bobbi%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20describes%20the%20moment%20that%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20her%20life.%20After%20telling%20her%20mom%20she%20didn't%20want%20to%20continue%20school%2C%20her%20mom%20asked%20what%20she%20would%20do%20if%20it%20was%20her%20birthday%2C%20and%20she%20could%20do%20anything%20she%20wanted.%20Brown%20said%20she'd%20head%20to%20a%20department%20store%20and%20play%20with%20makeup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20her%20mother%20offered%20advice%20that%20would%20shape%20her%20future%3A%20%26quot%3BThat's%20it.%20You%20should%20be%20a%20makeup%20artist%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20wrote%20that%20her%20mom%20told%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20exactly%20what%20she%20did%20until%20it%20led%20her%20to%20become%20a%20beauty%20founder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beauty%20founder%20said%20that%20recent%20grads%20should%20%26quot%3Btake%20the%20first%20entry-level%20job%26quot%3B%20they%20can%20find%20at%20a%20place%20where%20they%20could%20see%20themselves%20working%2C%20even%20if%20the%20role%20isn't%20quite%20what%20they%20envision%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20to%20surround%20yourself%20with%20what%20you%20love.%20For%20example%2C%20Brown%20said%20Jones%20Road%20Beauty%2C%20the%20clean%20beauty%20brand%20she%20launched%20in%202020%2C%20was%20looking%20to%20hire%20an%20office%20intern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20wasn't%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20interesting%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20requiring%20tasks%20like%20throwing%20out%20garbage%20or%20cleaning%20up%20after%20a%20photo%20shoot.%20But%20the%20woman%20who%20filled%20the%20role%20was%20%26quot%3Bspectacular%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20now%20a%20marketing%20manager%20at%20the%20company%2C%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20hired%20doesn't%20just%20happen%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20you%20walk%20in%20with%20a%20college%20degree%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22011bf56e-ae97-485f-9883-6f0641e144a1%5C%22%3EDon't%20stand%20still%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20selling%20her%20brand%20to%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20beauty%20conglomerates%2C%20Brown%20still%20found%20herself%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbobbi-brown-shares-exit-namesake-brand-aftermath-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ean%20era%20of%20uncertainty%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20unable%20to%20launch%20another%20brand%20because%20of%20the%20noncompete%20she%20had%20signed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20waiting%20for%20it%20to%20expire%2C%20she%20kept%20busy%2C%20creating%20a%20supplement%20brand%2C%20a%20curated%20shop%20at%20Lord%20%26amp%3B%20Taylor%2C%20and%20publishing%20a%20book.%20Eventually%2C%20she%20launched%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjones-road-bobbi-brown-advice-second-act-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esecond%20act%2C%20Jones%20Road%20Beauty%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStanding%20still%20is%20not%20an%20option%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20same%20mindset%20she%20encourages%20those%20just%20entering%20the%20job%20market%20to%20have.%20Brown%20said%20that%20she%20gets%20calls%20all%20the%20time%20from%20friends%2C%20relatives%2C%20and%20even%20her%20children%2C%20asking%20her%20to%20introduce%20them%20to%20someone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20that%20whether%20someone%20is%20trying%20to%20get%20into%20college%2C%20find%20a%20job%2C%20or%20meet%20their%20husband%2C%20they%20should%20look%20inward%20and%20see%20what%20can%20be%20done%20to%20improve%20their%20chances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20just%20sit%20there%20watching%20TV%20and%20expect%20the%20doorbell%20to%20ring%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbobbi-brown-shares-advice-recent-grads-entering-workforce-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773309241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b03c02441e48aec3a1d03a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbobbi-brown-shares-advice-recent-grads-entering-workforce-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bobbi%20Brown%20advises%20grads%20to%20take%20the%20first%20job%20they%20can%20find%20in%20an%20industry%20they%20want%20to%20work%20in.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2