ahead.%20While%20attendees%20%E2%80%94%20many%20young%2C%20and%20many%20European%20%E2%80%94%20schmoozed%20and%20visited%20booths%20dedicated%20to%20web%20hosting%20and%20fortune-cookie%20advertising%2C%20the%20phrase%20that%20kept%20popping%20up%20was%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20apps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20gonna%20be%20this%20massive%20convergence%20of%20Robinhood%2C%20Coinbase%2C%20and%20the%20gaming%20companies%20with%20super%20apps%2C%26quot%3B%20Roger%20Ehrenberg%2C%20an%20investor%2C%20said%20from%20the%20stage%20of%20the%20conference.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20mega-trend%20I%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuper%20apps%20are%20loosely%20defined%20as%20apps%20that%20subsume%20most%20of%20the%20reasons%20people%20look%20at%20their%20phones%20%E2%80%94%20messaging%2C%20shopping%20and%20payments%2C%20social%20media%20and%20news.%20Venture%20capitalists%20like%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20and%20tech-industry%20figures%20like%20Elon%20Musk%20have%20been%20predicting%20their%20rise%20for%20years.%20The%20model%20is%20China's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-superapp-wechat-best-feature-walkthrough-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWeChat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20combines%20social%20media%2C%20mobile%20payments%20and%20messaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20founders%20have%20said%20they%20want%20to%20be%20a%20one-stop%20shop.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fsam-bankman-fried%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20now-imprisoned%20crypto%20trader%2C%20once%20told%20investors%20that%20his%20vision%20for%20the%20exchange%20FTX%20was%20a%20platform%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20you%20can%20do%20anything%20you%20want%20with%20your%20next%20dollar.%20You%20can%20buy%20Bitcoin.%20You%20can%20buy%20a%20banana.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuper%20apps%20can%20create%20cross-selling%20opportunities.%20In%20a%202022%20blog%20post%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fa16z.com%2Fwhat-is-a-super-app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edescribed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Doordash%20and%20Uber%20rolling%20multiple%20services%20into%20the%20same%20app%20%E2%80%94%20food%20delivery%20and%20consumer%20goods%2C%20rides%2C%20and%20meals%20%E2%80%94%20as%20%26quot%3Bheaded%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20video%20app%20TikTok%20has%20become%20a%20massive%20presence%20in%20e-commerce%2C%20with%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-transformation-into-a-shopping-app-is-complete-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%20Shop%3C%2Fa%3E%20doing%20%24500%20million%20in%20business%20on%20Black%20Friday%20and%20adding%20major%20US%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20most%20Americans%20use%20a%20variety%20of%20apps%20to%20save%20and%20spend%20money%3A%20They%20might%20check%20Chase%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%20or%20Wells%20Fargo%20to%20see%20if%20their%20paycheck%20hit%2C%20and%20use%20a%20brokerage%20app%20like%20Fidelity%2C%20Wealthfront%20or%20Schwab%20to%20trade%20stocks%20or%20invest%20for%20retirement.%20Some%20might%20gamble%20using%20apps%20from%20FanDuel%2C%20BetMGM%2C%20DraftKings%2C%20PrizePicks%2C%20or%20any%20of%20dozens%20of%20other%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20American%20marketplace%20is%20more%20fractured%20than%20China's%2C%20where%20most%20people%20use%20WeChat.%20Despite%20Musk's%20desire%20for%20X%20to%20be%20an%20%26quot%3Beverything%20app%2C%26quot%3B%20only%20about%20a%20fifth%20of%20US%20adults%20use%20his%20social-media%20app%2C%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Finternet%2F2025%2F11%2F20%2Famericans-social-media-use-2025%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20year%20might%20be%20the%20year%20of%20the%20super%20app.%20When%20Musk%20acquired%20Twitter%20and%20rebranded%20it%20as%20X%20in%202022%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1577428272056389633%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20would%20become%20an%20%26quot%3Beverything%20app.%26quot%3B%20In%20recent%20weeks%2C%20he%20has%20teased%20the%20rollout%20of%20X%20Money%2C%20a%20way%20for%20people%20to%20save%20and%20send%20cash%20using%20his%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Kane%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Sporttrade%2C%20a%20sports%20betting%20exchange%20active%20in%20New%20Jersey%20with%20plans%20to%20go%20nationwide%2C%20said%20Robinhood%20has%20an%20edge%20in%20the%20race%20to%20build%20a%20super%20app.%20He%20said%20during%20a%20panel%20discussion%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20recently%20moved%20his%20main%20banking%20relationship%20to%20Robinhood%20and%20said%20the%20company%20offered%20an%20incentive%20to%20refinance%20his%20mortgage%20there%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20Kane%20said%2C%20users%20will%20%26quot%3Bhave%20one%20big%20wallet%20and%20trade%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobinhood%20and%20Kalshi%20announced%20a%20formal%20partnership%20in%20early%202025%2C%20and%20the%20investment%20app%20has%20historically%20been%20a%20major%20source%20of%20trades%20for%20the%20prediction%20market.%20One%20analyst%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.casino.org%2Fnews%2Frobinhood-prediction-markets-biz-on-pace-for-200m-in-revenue%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimated%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20fall%20that%2025%25%20to%2035%25%20of%20the%20money%20traded%20on%20Kalshi%20came%20from%20Robinhood%20users.%20Robinhood%20and%20the%20trading%20firm%20Susquehanna%20bought%20their%20own%20commodities%20exchange%20last%20year%20and%20plan%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20new%20prediction%20market%2C%20to%20be%20called%20Rothera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKane%20said%20he%20thinks%20Robinhood%20and%20other%20finance%20apps%20could%20eventually%20reduce%20the%20fees%20on%20sports%20trading%20to%20zero%20and%20use%20it%20as%20an%20on-ramp%20for%20young%20people%20who%20will%20generate%20income%20for%20Robinhood%20in%20different%20ways%2C%20like%20trading%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20drastically%20increase%20competition%20and%20require%20prediction%20market-only%20apps%20to%20spend%20much%20more%20than%20they%20currently%20do%20on%20marketing%2C%20new-user%20incentives%20and%20other%20customer%20acquisition%20costs%20for%20each%20new%20user%2C%20Kane%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrediction%20markets%20appear%20to%20have%20considered%20this%20possibility.%20Tarek%20Mansour%2C%20one%20of%20the%20co-founders%20of%20Kalshi%2C%20has%20said%20his%20company's%20ambition%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bfinancialize%20everything%20and%20create%20a%20tradable%20asset%20out%20of%20any%20difference%20in%20opinion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20the%20super%20app%20isn't%20guaranteed.%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20no%20one%20can%20seem%20to%20agree%20what%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20app%26quot%3B%20is.%20Last%20week%2C%20DraftKings%20used%20the%20term%20when%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.aboutdraftkings.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-details%2F2026%2FDraftKings-Outlines-Expanded-Growth-Strategy-and-Unveils-Plans-to-Launch-Super-App-DraftKings-Sports--Casino%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20would%20be%20merging%20its%20sports%2C%20predictions%2C%20lottery%20and%20casino%20apps.%20The%20company%20isn't%20going%20into%20banking%2C%20instant%20messaging%2C%20or%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrediction%20markets%2C%20gambling%2C%20and%20finance%20apps%20also%20compete%20on%20dimensions%20beyond%20commissions%20and%20fees%2C%20like%20user%20experience.%20Online%20gaming%20veterans%20often%20joke%20that%20Betfair%2C%20a%20long-running%20British%20sports%20exchange%2C%20could%20pick%20up%20more%20users%20if%20it%20updated%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20sports%20bettors%20are%20very%20provably%20price-insensitive%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiftycentdollars.substack.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdhi%20Rajaprabhakaran%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20Kalshi%20trader%20who%20writes%20about%20prediction%20markets%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20I%20think%20fees%20are%20going%20to%20increase%20over%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20super%20apps%20enter%20the%20picture%20in%20a%20real%20way%2C%20some%20industry%20analysts%20think%20prediction%20markets%20have%20a%20real%20shot%20at%20competing%20for%20users'%20attention%20and%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20impossible%20to%20ignore%20the%20prevalence%20and%20rise%20in%20prediction%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Joseph%20Solosky%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20for%20sports%20betting%20at%20NASCAR.%20%26quot%3BIn%20short%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20a%20passing%20fad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Know%20more%3F%20Reach%20Jack%20Newsham%20via%20email%20(%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajnewsham%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ejnewsham%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E)%20or%20via%20Signal%20(%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B13149711627%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E%2B1-314-971-1627%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E).%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20device%2C%20and%20nonwork%20WiFi%3B%20here's%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecure-news-tips%3Futm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_source%3Dyahoo.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eour%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnext-summit-prediction-markets-super-apps-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773308221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b1cefd4d65ec517529dbe4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnext-summit-prediction-markets-super-apps-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Did%20you%20think%20prediction%20markets%20were%20all%20the%20rage%3F%20Time%20to%20learn%20about%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20apps.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jnewsham%40insider.com%20(Jack%20Newsham)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnext-summit-prediction-markets-super-apps-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Army%20officers%20say%20battlefield%20leaders%20facing%20new%20drone%20threats%20have%20another%20problem%20to%20deal%20with%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20information%20overload%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224680%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Army%20soldiers%20with%20the%202d%20Cavalry%20Regiment%20are%20absorbing%20lessons%20learned%20from%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20as%20they%20train%20with%20Ukrainian%20troops%20and%20test%20new%20methods.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b1a61a4d65ec517529d538%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222901%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Army%20soldiers%20with%20the%202d%20Cavalry%20Regiment%20are%20absorbing%20lessons%20learned%20from%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20as%20they%20train%20with%20Ukrainian%20troops%20and%20test%20new%20methods.%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Army%20photo%20by%20Sgt.%20Rebecca%20Call%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20information%20flows%20on%20modern%20battlefields%20can%20be%20overwhelming%20for%20commanders.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EArmy%20leaders%20warn%20of%20%26quot%3Bcognitive%20overload%26quot%3B%20for%20commanders%20on%20the%20ground%20facing%20new%20and%20traditional%20threats.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20battlefield%20is%20changing%20dramatically%20amid%20new%20drone%20and%20EW%20threats.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20an%20explosion%20in%20new%20kinds%20of%20battlefield%20tech%2C%20from%20all%20kinds%20of%20drones%20to%20the%20systems%20and%20sensors%20being%20built%20to%20defeat%20them%2C%20commanders%20at%20all%20levels%20are%20grappling%20with%20the%20growing%20challenge%20of%20information%20overload.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Army%20absorbs%20lessons%20from%20Ukraine%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20seeing%20a%20cognitive%20overload%20on%20the%20ground%20for%20commanders%20who%20have%20to%20fight%20both%20the%20ground%20fight%20and%20the%20air%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Maj.%20Andrew%20Kang%2C%20the%20fire%20support%20officer%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dmh9RtpZPpVo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2nd%20Cavalry%20Regiment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20during%20a%20media%20roundtable%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Stryker%20unit%20based%20in%20Germany%20is%20experimenting%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fin-future-wars-army-may-send-robots-to-rescue-wounded-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20training%20Ukrainian%20troops%20on%20American%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20inundation%20of%20information%20is%20pushing%20the%20Army%20to%20rely%20more%20heavily%20on%20technology%20to%20filter%20and%20prioritize%20data%20before%20it%20reaches%20a%20commander%2C%20Kang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20threat%20stands%20today%2C%20a%20web%20of%20sensors%20is%20critical%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-level-drone-warfare-new-risk-civilians-ukraine-russia-iran-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecombating%20enemy%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kang%20said.%20Available%20sensors%20include%20acoustic%20detectors%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-showing-us-troops-fight-hide-in-electromagnetic-spectrum-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eelectromagnetic%20spectrum%3C%2Fa%3E%20monitoring%2C%20live%20video%20feeds%2C%20and%20other%20intelligence%20inputs%20flowing%20in%20from%20across%20the%20force.%20Together%2C%20they%20generate%20a%20stream%20of%20alerts%20that%20must%20be%20assessed%20and%20acted%20on%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20it%20is%20landing%20increasingly%20on%20officers%20in%20the%20field%2C%20who%20are%20expected%20to%20synchronize%20artillery%2C%20aircraft%2C%20and%20ground%20maneuver%20while%20simultaneously%20tracking%20drone%20threats%20and%20managing%20electronic%20signatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20allows%20that%20decision-making%20is%20the%20input%2C%20the%20ingest%20of%20all%20that%20data%2C%20to%20optimize%20the%20right%20defeat%20mechanism%20against%20the%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Capt.%20Gabriel%20Glazer%2C%20the%202nd%20Cavalry%20Regiment's%20signal%20officer.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20where%20I%20think%20we%20keep%20harping%20on%20the%20network%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20has%20been%20increasingly%20looking%20into%20solutions%20for%20synthesizing%20large%20quantities%20of%20battlefield%20data%20into%20manageable%20packages%20for%20command%20and%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22961fb235-94ec-42ca-a774-b9fbfae20257%5C%22%3EA%20changing%20battlefield%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20easy%20to%20focus%20on%20drones%20and%20counter-drone%20systems%20as%20defining%20features%20of%20modern%20warfare%2C%20Kang%20said%2C%20but%20it's%20more%20than%20that.%20An%20equally%20pressing%20shift%2C%20leaving%20less%20time%20for%20decision-making%20and%20processing%2C%20is%20the%20operational%20tempo%20of%20fighting%2C%20which%20he%20described%20in%20Ukraine%20as%20%26quot%3Balmost%20incomprehensible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20pace%20is%20reshaping%20not%20only%20how%20units%20fight%2C%20but%20also%20how%20they%20physically%20organize%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20growing%20concern%20is%20signature%20management%2C%20Glazer%20said%2C%20a%20unit's%20ability%20to%20control%20the%20electronic%20and%20visual%20signals%20it%20emits.%20In%20a%20battlefield%20saturated%20with%20drones%20and%20electronic%20surveillance%2C%20large%20centralized%20headquarters%20have%20become%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Global%20War%20on%20Terror%2C%20planning%20coordination%20often%20unfolded%20in%20bustling%2C%20centralized%20command%20posts%20where%20the%20commander%20and%20staff%20%E2%80%94%20intelligence%2C%20logistics%2C%20and%20operations%20troops%20%E2%80%94%20worked%20side%20by%20side.%20In%20new%20combat%20environments%20shaped%20by%20drones%20and%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%20warfare%2C%20that%20model%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-war-with-iran-shows-unseen-battle-vital-modern-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eincreasingly%20untenable%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20roundtable%2C%202nd%20Cavalry%20Regiment%20commander%20Col.%20Donald%20Neal%20recalled%20serving%20as%20a%20brigade%20executive%20officer%20a%20decade%20ago%20in%20a%20sprawling%20command%20headquarters%2C%20which%20he%20likened%20to%20a%20football%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20amid%20exercises%20against%20mock%20enemy%20forces%20capable%20of%20wielding%20drones%20as%20readily%20available%20reconnaissance%20tools%2C%20and%20electronic%20warfare%20and%20sensor%20systems%2C%20headquarters%20must%20be%20a%20fraction%20of%20that%20size%2C%20and%20more%20dispersed%20to%20survive%20%E2%80%94%20rather%20than%20operate%20from%20a%20single%20large%20hub%2C%20units%20now%20break%20apart%20their%20command%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20having%20one%20massive%2C%20we%20had%20four%20different%20ones%20spread%20sometimes%20up%20to%2030%20kilometers%20away%20from%20each%20other%20to%20be%20survivable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20recent%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlazer%20said%20understanding%20the%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%20can%20no%20longer%20be%20confined%20to%20senior%20officers.%20Junior%20troops%20%E2%80%94%20often%20the%20most%20exposed%20%E2%80%94%20need%20to%20grasp%20how%20their%20radios%2C%20emissions%2C%20and%20digital%20systems%20can%20make%20them%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20regiment's%20experimentation%20has%20already%20changed%20how%20soldiers%20communicate%20and%20move%2C%20and%20those%20adjustments%20have%20%26quot%3Bseeped%20into%20every%20single%20echelon%20of%20the%20regiment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmy-leaders-warn-modern-warfare-is-overwhelming-commanders-with-data-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773308161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b1a64c4d65ec517529d540%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmy-leaders-warn-modern-warfare-is-overwhelming-commanders-with-data-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Army%20officers%20say%20modern%20drone%20warfare%20is%20creating%20%26quot%3Bcognitive%20overload%26quot%3B%20and%20new%20tech%20is%20needed%20to%20help%20sort%20it%20all.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbaker%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmy-leaders-warn-modern-warfare-is-overwhelming-commanders-with-data-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gamers%20just%20want%20to%20chill%20out%20and%20farm%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20sparking%20a%20surprise%20rally%20in%20Nintendo%20stock%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pok%C3%A9mon%20Pokopia%20on%20Nintendo%20Switch%202%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b1d912a96e437d6eb82b1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22681%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPok%C3%A9mon%20Pokopia%20on%20Nintendo%20Switch%202.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Keeble%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BPok%C3%A9mon%20Pokopia%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20life-simulation%20game%20that%20heavily%20features%20farming%2C%20has%20been%20a%20surprise%20hit%20for%20Nintendo.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company's%20stock%20has%20taken%20a%20hit%20as%20the%20global%20memory%20shortage%20has%20crunched%20Switch%202%20margins.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20%26quot%3BPok%C3%A9mon%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20new%20%26quot%3BSuper%20Mario%26quot%3B%20movie%20have%20analysts%20getting%20bullish%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou've%20had%20a%20long%20day%20at%20work%20and%20you're%20looking%20to%20unwind.%20You%20drop%20a%20mint%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-ceo-tony-xu-key-advantage-over-amazon-grocery-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDoorDash%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20settle%20into%20the%20couch%20for%20some%20video%20gaming.%20The%20intensity%20of%20a%20first-person%20shooter%20or%20racing%20game%20isn't%20your%20vibe%20right%20now.%20You%20want%20to%20relax%2C%20so%20you%20fire%20up%20%26quot%3BPok%C3%A9mon%20Pokopia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20around%20the%20world%2C%20people%20are%20going%20through%20this%20thought%20process.%20The%20desire%20to%20decompress%20is%20why%20so-called%20cozy%20games%20like%20the%20new%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpokemon-cards-parents-guide-collecting-cost-gift-giving-products-value-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPok%C3%A9mon%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20similar%20to%20%26quot%3BAnimal%20Crossing%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BStardew%20Valley%26quot%3B%20before%20it%20%E2%80%94%20are%20so%20popular.%20Sometimes%20you%20just%20want%20to%20chill%20out%20and%20tend%20to%20your%20digital%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20mentality%20has%20created%20a%20surprise%20hit%20for%20Nintendo%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20company%20badly%20needs%20a%20boost.%20Released%20exclusively%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnintendo-switch-2-launch-event-release-lines-stores-cities-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESwitch%202%20console%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%2C%20the%20game%20quickly%20sold%20out%20at%20several%20major%20US%20retailers.%20Demand%20was%20so%20high%20that%20Amazon%20even%20temporarily%20raised%20prices%20%E2%80%94%20something%20it%20rarely%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENintendo%20stock%20was%20rewarded%20with%20a%2015%25%20surge%20across%20two%20days%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gain%20was%20also%20partially%20fueled%20by%20the%20release%20of%20the%20final%20trailer%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BSuper%20Mario%20Galaxy%20Movie%2C%26quot%3B%20due%20out%20on%20April%201.%20Buzz%20is%20strong%20heading%20into%20the%20sequel%20after%20the%20first%20installment%20made%20%241.4%20billion%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20the%20recent%20wins%2C%20the%20chart%20below%20shows%20that%20Nintendo%20stock%20still%20has%20far%20to%20go%20to%20recover%20its%202025%20peak.%20Shares%20are%20still%20down%20more%20than%2030%25%20from%20record%20highs%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FAXEbx%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FAXEbx%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ENintendo%20has%20fallen%20victim%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-deepmind-demis-hassabis-memory-shortage-ai-supply-chain-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20memory-chip%20shortage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20hiked%20prices%20for%20chips%20and%20squeezed%20margins%20on%20products%20that%20rely%20on%20them%2C%20like%20the%20Switch%202.%20The%20same%20issue%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmemory-shortage-chips-cost-laptop-pc-prices-increase-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20also%20become%20a%20hurdle%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20smartphone-makers%20like%20Apple%20and%20other%20consumer-electronics%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStock%20analysts%20are%20starting%20to%20come%20around%20on%20Nintendo's%20comeback%20story%20following%20%26quot%3BPok%C3%A9mon%20Pokopia's%26quot%3B%20runaway%20success.%20And%20in%20addition%20to%20moving%20a%20bunch%20of%20%2470%20game%20units%2C%20the%20company%20is%20expected%20to%20sell%20more%20of%20its%20%24450%20flagship%20console.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bstealth%20hit%26quot%3B%20will%20%26quot%3Bdrive%20Nintendo%20Switch%202%20adoption%20amid%20memory%20cost%20headwinds%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20big%20drag%20on%20the%20stock%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20Jefferies%20analyst%20Atul%20Goyal%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20client%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20a%20buy%20rating%20on%20the%20stock%2C%20and%20a%2012-month%20price%20target%20that%20calls%20for%20a%20114%25%20gain%20from%20Wednesday's%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%20Intelligence%20analyst%20Nathan%20Naidu%20points%20out%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BSuper%20Mario%20Galaxy%20Movie%26quot%3B%20will%20primarily%20impact%20Nintendo's%20higher-margin%20software%20division%2C%20giving%20it%20even%20more%20upside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoyal%20says%20the%20movie%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bnext%20major%20indicator%20of%20Nintendo's%20transmedia%20momentum.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%207-year-old%20son%20and%20I%20will%20be%20ready.%20As%20card-carrying%20Switch%202%20owners%2C%20it's%20our%20most-anticipated%20movie%20of%20the%20year.%20The%20question%20is%20whether%20there%20are%20enough%20enthusiasts%20like%20us%20out%20there%20to%20lift%20Nintendo%20shares%20back%20to%20former%20heights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpokemon-pokopia-super-mario-galaxy-movie-nintendo-stock-price-impact-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773308102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b1d924a7a4f9df67ba31ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpokemon-pokopia-super-mario-galaxy-movie-nintendo-stock-price-impact-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pok%C3%A9mon%20Pokopia%20has%20been%20a%20stealth%20hit%20for%20Nintendo%2C%20and%20investors%20are%20also%20excited%20about%20the%20new%20Super%20Mario%20movie.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jciolli%40businessinsider.com%20(Joe%20Ciolli)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpokemon-pokopia-super-mario-galaxy-movie-nintendo-stock-price-impact-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blue%20Owl%20keeps%20chasing%20AI%20infrastructure%20deals%20and%20is%20writing%20the%20loans%20to%20back%20them%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20walking%20by%20a%20sign%20with%20Blue%20Owl's%20logo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b21683a7a4f9df67ba332f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlue%20Owl%20Capital%3Cp%3EBrendan%20McDermid%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20learned%20of%20three%20large%20loans%20Blue%20Owl%20recently%20placed%20against%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20deals%20show%20how%20the%20firm%20is%20broadening%20its%20exposure%20to%20lucrative%20digital%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lending%20comes%20as%20the%20firm%20has%20faced%20investor%20withdrawals%20elsewhere%20in%20its%20portfolio.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-bosses-software-bets-blackstone-apollo-ares-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBlue%20Owl%20Capital%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20doubling%20down%20on%20artificial%20intelligence%20infrastructure%20investments%20%E2%80%94%20including%20loans%20to%20two%20more%20data%20centers%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Wall%20Street%20investment%20and%20credit%20firm%20raised%20nearly%20%2410%20billion%20for%20digital%20infrastructure%2C%20primarily%20for%20ownership%20interests%20in%20data%20center%20projects.%20The%20company%20has%20also%20expanded%20its%20lending%20to%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Owl%2C%20based%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20recently%20agreed%20to%20provide%20%24240%20million%20of%20financing%20for%20a%20data%20center%20in%20Minneapolis%20that%20was%20purchased%20by%20investors%20Cloud%20Capital%20and%20Arcapita%20Group%2C%20according%20to%20two%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20transaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20plans%20to%20both%20invest%20in%20and%20lend%20to%20a%20recently%20announced%20large%20data%20center%20development%20in%20Wichita%20Falls%2C%20Texas%2C%20being%20built%20by%20the%20Dallas-based%20firm%20Skybox%20Datacenters%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20structure%20of%20that%20project.%20Blue%20Owl's%20role%20as%20a%20lender%20in%20that%20development%20hasn't%20previously%20been%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Owl%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20the%20firm%20disclosed%20that%20it%20holds%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-owl-financing-lancaster-data-center-coreweave-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%24500%20million%20loan%20%3C%2Fa%3Econnected%20to%20a%20data%20center%20being%20built%20in%20Lancaster%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20for%20the%20AI%20cloud%20provider%20CoreWeave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20said%20they%20see%20the%20firm's%20growing%20focus%20on%20debt%20as%20a%20way%20for%20it%20to%20broaden%20its%20exposure%20to%20lucrative%20digital%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20be%20able%20to%20evaluate%20the%20efficacy%20of%20any%20deal%2C%20and%20they%20are%20definitely%20smart%20credit%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20Glenn%20Schorr%2C%20a%20research%20analyst%20at%20Evercore%20ISI%20who%20covers%20Blue%20Owl%2C%20said%20of%20the%20company's%20data%20center%20lending.%20%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20complete%20sense%20conceptually%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20success%20in%20data%20center%20investment%20is%20a%20contrast%20to%20headwinds%20being%20felt%20elsewhere%20in%20its%20portfolio.%20In%20the%20fourth%20quarter%2C%20the%20company%20was%20hit%20with%20an%20increase%20in%20client%20withdrawals%20from%20two%20of%20its%20credit%20funds%2C%20in%20part%20because%20both%20hold%20collections%20of%20loans%20tied%20to%20software%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20models%20have%20made%20rapid%20strides%2C%20enabling%20users%20to%20build%20sophisticated%20applications%20with%20simple%20prompts%2C%20stoking%20fears%20that%20software%20businesses%20could%20be%20upended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20credit%20business%20manages%20about%20%24160%20billion%20in%20assets%20and%20is%20the%20largest%20segment%20of%20the%20firm's%20portfolio.%20The%20company%20has%20disclosed%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.blueowl.com%2Fsolutions%2Finvestment-strategy-real-assets-digital-infrastructure%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2415.4%20billion%20of%20digital%20infrastructure%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fe930eaf-1e81-4de3-b5e2-9eacba82af77%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFocus%20on%20digital%20infrastructure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Owl%20executives%20have%20said%20the%20firm%20plans%20to%20dramatically%20grow%20its%20data%20center%20portfolio.%20Much%20of%20that%20activity%20has%20focused%20on%20acquiring%20ownership%20stakes%20in%20deals%20and%20development%20projects.%20Last%20year%2C%20it%20agreed%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20to%20invest%20%242.45%20billion%20to%20purchase%20an%2080%25%20ownership%20interest%20in%20a%20large%20data%20center%20campus%20being%20built%20for%20Meta%20in%20Louisiana%2C%20expected%20to%20cost%20%2430%20billion%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20through%20the%20data%20center%20platform%20it%20owns%2C%20Stack%20Infrastructure%2C%20is%20building%20large-scale%20data%20facilities%20in%20Texas%20and%20New%20Mexico%2C%20and%20recently%20announced%20it%20would%20develop%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stackinfra.com%2Fabout%2Fnews-press%2Fpress-releases%2Fstack-infrastructure-announces-data-center-developments-supporting-economic-growth-in-louisiana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2412%20billion%20campus%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Amazon%20in%20Louisiana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20eyeing%20even%20more%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20person%20involved%20in%20the%20sale%20of%20a%20data%20center%20development%20land%20site%20outside%20of%20Birmingham%2C%20Alabama%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Blue%20Owl%20has%20expressed%20interest%20in%20acquiring%20the%20property.%20The%20person%20said%20the%20firm%20was%20one%20of%20several%20interested%20parties%20and%20that%20the%20sales%20effort%20for%20the%20site%20was%20at%20a%20preliminary%20stage%20and%20may%20not%20proceed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fourth%20quarter%2C%20Blue%20Owl%20closed%20a%20%241.7%20billion%20fundraise%20for%20a%20new%20private%20wealth-focused%20vehicle%20called%20Blue%20Owl%20Digital%20Infrastructure%20Trust%20that%20will%20acquire%20data%20centers.%20Last%20May%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.blueowl.com%2Fnews%2Fblue-owl-capital-announces-7-billion-final-close-digital-infrastructure-fund%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20had%20separately%20raised%20its%20third%20digital%20infrastructure%20fund%2C%20with%20%247%20billion%20of%20capital%2C%20almost%20double%20its%20initial%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20its%20fourth-quarter%20earnings%20call%2C%20the%20company's%20co-CEO%20Marc%20Lipschultz%20said%20another%20digital%20infrastructure%20fund%20would%20be%20raised%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20saw%20the%20great%20success%20we%20had%20in%20raising%20our%20latest%20Digital%20Infrastructure%20Fund%20III%2C%20which%20we%20already%20are%20heavily%20invested%2C%20so%20we'll%20be%20back%20this%20year%20with%20Digital%20Infrastructure%20Fund%20IV%2C%26quot%3B%20Lipschultz%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%20transcript%20of%20the%20call%20from%20AlphaSense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e49b5bbe-f636-42b5-8f9c-4e5660a5860a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECredit%20fears%20and%20growing%20withdrawals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fourth%20quarter%2C%20two%20funds%20in%20Blue%20Owl's%20credit%20portfolio%20saw%20elevated%20withdrawals.%20Blue%20Owl%20Technology%20Income%20Corporation%2C%20a%20roughly%20%243.5%20billion%20fund%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1869453%2F000186945326000017%2Fortic-20251231.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereceived%20redemptions%3C%2Fa%3E%20totaling%2015.6%25%20of%20its%20net%20asset%20value%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20three%20times%20the%20fund's%20quarterly%20withdrawal%20limit%20of%205%25.%20Another%20fund%2C%20Blue%20Owl%20Credit%20Income%20Corporation%2C%20saw%20roughly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1812554%2F000162828026003929%2Focic-scheduletoajanuary2026.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241%20billion%20of%20redemptions%20%3C%2Fa%3Etotaling%20about%205.2%25%20of%20the%20fund%2C%20which%20was%20also%20in%20excess%20of%20its%205%25%20withdrawal%20cap.%20Although%20the%20redemption%20requests%20were%20above%20the%20funds'%20exit%20thresholds%2C%20Blue%20Owl%20met%20them.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-crisis-blue-owl-wall-street-owl-stock-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20Some%20analysts%20have%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20concerns%20that%20drove%20the%20withdrawals%20are%20overblown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20retreat%20among%20investors%20from%20private%20credit%20has%20reached%20beyond%20Blue%20Owl.%20Blackstone%20reported%20that%20a%20private%20credit%20fund%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstones-bcred-redemptions-blue-owl-private-credit-investors-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithdrawal%20requests%3C%2Fa%3E%20totaling%207.9%25%20in%20the%20first%20quarter.%20It%20also%20met%20those%20redemptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20collection%20of%20private%20credit%20funds%20tracked%20by%20Robert%20A.%20Stanger%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20saw%20average%20withdrawals%20of%204.84%25%20of%20their%20net%20asset%20value%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%2C%20more%20than%20double%20the%20third%20quarter%20average%20of%201.75%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20the%20cycle%20of%20upcoming%20elevated%20redemptions%20for%20all%20of%20the%20BDCs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Michael%20Covello%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20at%20Stanger%2C%20referring%20to%20business%20development%20companies%2C%20a%20structure%20used%20by%20many%20private%20credit%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-owl-ai-infrastructure-investments-loans-equity-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773308101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b21975a7a4f9df67ba3360%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-owl-ai-infrastructure-investments-loans-equity-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Blue%20Owl%20has%20become%20one%20of%20Wall%20Street's%2