5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eharsh%2C%20unforgiving%20Arctic%2C%20though%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaj.%20Robin%20McArthur%2C%20a%20battery%20commander%20with%20a%20unit%20in%20the%20British%20Army's%2029th%20Commando%20Regiment%20Royal%20Artillery%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20at%20a%20firing%20range%20in%20northern%20Norway%20last%20month%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-war-chernobyl-ukraine-most-radioactive-place-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussian%20invasion%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20demonstrated%20the%20crucial%20need%20to%20integrate%20drones%20with%20area%20fires%2C%20such%20as%20artillery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheap%2C%20expendable%20drones%20are%20increasingly%20available%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-troops-air-defenses-shaheds-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebattlefield%20surveillance%20and%20reconnaissance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20McArthur's%20troops%20have%20been%20training%20to%20use%20these%20tools%20to%20collect%20targeting%20data%20and%20relay%20that%20information%20to%20the%20firing%20team%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tactic%20proven%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20McArthur%20said%2C%20the%20drones%20his%20unit%20has%20been%20using%20are%20often%20designed%20for%20more%20temperate%20climates%20and%20are%20easily%20affected%20by%20the%20brutal%20Arctic%20environment%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-troops-cant-let-guns-get-too-warm-frozen-battlefields-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etechnology%20tends%20to%20struggle%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20cold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20part%20of%20the%20appeal%2C%20actually%2C%20of%20traditional%20artillery%20over%20the%20attack%20drones%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22British%20forces%20prepare%20to%20fire%20their%20artillery%20in%20Norway%20in%20February%202026.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b154eea7a4f9df67ba21d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBritish%20forces%20prepare%20to%20fire%20their%20artillery%20in%20Norway.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20not%20affected%20by%20weather%20and%20the%20environment%20is%20a%20great%20big%20chunk%20of%20metal%20coming%20toward%20your%20face%20that's%20fired%20out%20of%20one%20of%20these%20guns%2C%26quot%3B%20McArthur%20said%2C%20referencing%20his%20105mm%20light%20howitzer%20and%20the%20high-explosive%20shells%20it%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20commandos%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-arctic-artillery-forces-learn-dig-hide-move-dodge-drones-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efired%20artillery%20in%20Setermoen%3C%2Fa%3E%20alongside%20Norwegian%20soldiers%20and%20US%20Marines%20as%20part%20of%20Cold%20Response%2026%2C%20a%20military%20exercise%20led%20by%20Oslo%20that%20trains%20NATO%20forces%20for%20Arctic%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENATO%20is%20investing%20more%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwestern-forces-arctic-cold-is-one-of-their-toughest-enemies-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EArctic%20defense%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20readiness%20as%20alliance%20officials%20grow%20increasingly%20concerned%20about%20Russian%20and%20Chinese%20activity%20across%20the%20High%20North.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20training%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-finland-trains-nato-arctic-warfare-snowmobiles-skis-lasers-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efight%20on%20frozen%20battlefields%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20NATO%20forces%20are%20incorporating%20lessons%20about%20modern%20combat%20that%20they've%20learned%20from%20watching%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20a%20mix%20of%20high-tech%20and%20industrial%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaj.%20Ka