ction%20markets%20hinders%20trust.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPrediction%20markets%20have%20exploded%20in%20popularity%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20and%20with%20the%20boom%20has%20come%20increased%20scrutiny%20on%20what%20people%20are%20betting%20on%E2%80%94and%20when%20they're%20betting.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drama%20kicked%20off%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fritchie-torres-insider-trading-ban-polymarket-government-officials-maduro-venezuela-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20well-timed%20bet%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20US%20military's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnicolas-maduro-manhattan-court-charges-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Earrest%20of%3C%2Fa%3E%20Venezuelan%20President%20Nicholas%20Maduro%20in%20January.%20The%20Iran%20War%20this%20month%20has%20also%20produced%20a%20flood%20of%20available%20wagers%20on%20the%20conflict%2C%20leading%20to%20worries%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprediction-markets-polymarket-kalshi-venezuela-raid-bet-insider-trading-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einsiders%20in%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20be%20profiting%20from%20information%20before%20it%20goes%20public.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Center%20for%20American%20Progress%2C%20a%20nonpartisan%20think%20tank%2C%20said%20in%20an%20analysis%20published%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20use%20of%20crypto%20is%20weighing%20on%20public%20trust%20in%20prediction%20markets.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20blockchain%20analytics%20platform%20Bubblemaps%2C%20the%20Iranian%20attack%20bets%20were%20funded%20by%20digital%20wallets%20opened%20within%2024%20hours%20of%20the%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BSimilarly%2C%20an%20anonymous%20Polymarket%20user%20placed%20a%20bet%20hours%20before%20the%20U.S.%20military%20capture%20of%20Maduro%20on%20January%203%2C%20predicting%20that%20he%20would%20be%20out%20of%20power%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlexandra%20Thornton%2C%20the%20report's%20author%20and%20senior%20director%20of%20financial%20regulation%20at%20the%20CAP%2C%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20about%20how%20she%20sees%20crypto%20as%20problematic%20for%20prediction%20markets%20like%20Polymarket%2C%20which%20is%20a%20crypto-based%20betting%20site.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThornton%20said%20that%20the%20problem%2C%20in%20her%20view%2C%20is%20the%20anonymity%20offered%20by%20crypto.%20The%20fact%20that%20users%20can%20place%20bets%20behind%20the%20veil%20of%20an%20online%20pseudonym%20made%20possible%20by%20blockchain%20makes%20it%20too%20easy%20for%20those%20with%20insider%20information%20to%20bet%20on%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%20we%20don't%20want%20crypto%20facilitating%20illicit%20activity%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20used%20to%20avoid%20sanctions%20or%20to%20make%20bets%20using%20inside%20government%20information%2C%20which%20is%20not%20proven%2C%20but%20what%20many%20people%20are%20concerned%20is%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20yet%20another%20way%20that%20anonymous%20crypto%20transactions%20can%20facilitate%20illicit%20activity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkhamenei-prediction-markets-kalshi-polymarket-insider-trading-outrage-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAccusations%20of%20insider%20trading%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20prediction%20markets%20have%20surged%20this%20month%2C%20with%20social%20media%20awash%20in%20outraged%20comments%20about%20bettors%20who%20made%20money%20on%20the%20Iran%20war%20and%20the%20killing%20of%20Iran's%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ali%20Khamenei.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Thornton%20said%20that%20the%20accusations%20of%20insider%20trading%20remain%20unproven%20as%20of%20now%2C%20she%20added%20that%20she%20thinks%20crypto%20could%20make%20it%20tempting%20for%20government%20insiders%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20their%20non-public%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20January%20blog%20post%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.polymarket.com%2Fp%2Fpie-hard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolymarket%20profiled%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20trader%20who%20had%20used%20the%20Pentagon%20Pizza%20Index%20to%20time%20a%20successful%20bet%20on%20the%20Venezuela%20attacks.%20The%20indicator%20claims%20to%20be%20able%20to%20gauge%20the%20timing%20of%20military%20action%20by%20monitoring%20the%20late-night%20delivery%20of%20pizzas%20to%20the%20Pentagon.%20Thornton%20said%20she%20wasn't%20convinced%20by%20the%20explanation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolymarket%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-betting-markets-insider-trading-polymarket-venezuela-iran-war-bets-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773307801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b1ced6a96e437d6eb829a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-betting-markets-insider-trading-polymarket-venezuela-iran-war-bets-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20report%20from%20the%20Center%20for%20American%20Progress%20highlights%20the%20potential%20for%20crypto%20to%20enable%20insider%20trading%20in%20prediction%20markets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sobrient%40insider.com%20(Samuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-betting-markets-insider-trading-polymarket-venezuela-iran-war-bets-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Suriya%20became%20one%20of%20the%20most%20versatile%20actors%20in%20Tamil%20cinema%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773307717000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129501123%2Cimgsize-61350.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesof