om%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Fwhat-happened-to-devi-after-never-have-i-ever-finale-heres-what-maitreyi-ramakrishnan-thinks%2Farticleshow%2F129500777.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Snap's%20director%20of%20product%20design%20doesn't%20care%20about%20your%20degree.%20She%20wants%20to%20see%20what%20you've%20built.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Imani%20Ritchards%2C%20Snap's%20director%20of%20product%20design%2C%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b1ab294d65ec517529d616%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20hard%20to%20train%20someone%20to%20have%20good%20ideas%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Imani%20Ritchards%2C%20Snap's%20director%20of%20product%20design.%3Cp%3ESnap%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESnap's%20director%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-is-influencing-product-design-2024-6%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eproduct%20design%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider%20what%20she%20looks%20for%20in%20a%20candidate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDesign%20degrees%20aren't%20important%20to%20Imani%20Ritchards.%20She%20cares%20more%20about%20creative%20risk-taking.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20school%20can%20help%20you%20learn%20the%20process%2C%20she%20said%20AI%20tools%20now%20allow%20people%20to%20get%20together%20and%20simply%20%26quot%3Bmake%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EImani%20Ritchards%20is%20an%20ideas%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20of%20product%20design%20at%20Snap%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20Snapchat%2C%20doesn't%20care%20much%20about%20your%20degree%20or%20your%20accolades.%20Mere%20hours%20before%20our%20chat%20at%20Snap's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnapchat-leaves-san-francisco-office-lease-closed-during-snap-restructuring-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESanta%20Monica%3C%2Fa%3E%20headquarters%2C%20Ritchards%20interviewed%20a%20designer.%20But%20they%20didn't%20have%20a%20fancy%20design%20degree%2C%20they%20were%20a%20chemical%20engineering%20major.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20Ritchards%20does%20care%20about%20is%20creativity%20and%20how%20they%20use%20it.%20She%20looks%20for%20candidates%20with%20an%20%26quot%3Bopenness%20to%20take%20creative%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20me%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20portfolio%20to%20back%20it%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20of%20a%20product%20designer%20is%20rapidly%20changing.%20With%20the%20right%20suite%20of%20AI%20tools%2C%20anyone%20can%20build%20an%20app%20that%20looks%20fine.%20What%20takes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fux-designer-works-3-jobs-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ean%20app's%20UX%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20fine%20to%20great%3F%20That's%20the%20question%20dozens%20of%20tech%20companies%20across%20the%20country%20are%20considering%20as%20they%20hire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERitchards%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider%20her%20rules%20for%20design%20hiring%20these%20days.%20The%20first%3A%20having%20a%20design%20degree%20isn't%20as%20helpful%20as%20it%20used%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20really%20helpful%20about%20school%20is%20that%20it%20helps%20you%20learn%20the%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20there%20are%20so%20many%20ways%20to%20learn%20the%20process%20and%2C%20especially%20with%20AI%20tools%20today%2C%20you%20can%20just%20get%20your%20friends%20together%20and%20make%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20cares%20more%20that%20candidates%20have%20built%20and%20tested%20something.%20Feedback%20is%20important%20here%2C%20she%20said%2C%20and%20ideally%20it%20comes%20from%20real%20users.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20do%20that%20without%20a%20formal%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20Ritchards%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20more%20technical%20skills%2C%20they%20can%20often%20be%20learned%20on%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20say%20someone%20is%20a%20great%20ideator%2C%20but%20maybe%20their%20visual%20design%20skills%20need%20some%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Ritchards%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20train%20them%20up%20in%20those%20skills%2C%20but%20it's%20so%20hard%20to%20train%20someone%20to%20have%20good%20ideas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20isn't%20just%20making%20people%20faster%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20causing%20some%20companies%20to%20slim%20down.%20Some%20AI%20doomers%20have%20predicted%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadobe-ai-firefly-kill-graphic-designer-jobs-cut-seat-sales-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eend%20of%20design%20as%20we%20know%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20that%20one%20person%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-agents-management-structure-org-chart-consulting-firms-mckinsey-ibm-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eseries%20of%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20enough%20to%20build%20a%20successful%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20Ritchards%20think%20about%20this%20mindset%3F%20She%20doesn't%20take%20much%20stock%20in%20predictions.%20%26quot%3BThe%20industry%20is%20changing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20things%20will%20evolve%20is%20not%20something%20anyone%20can%20really%20predict.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20does%20affect%20how%20she%20interviews%20candidates%2C%20though.%20Ritchards%20is%20a%20fan%20of%20AI%20tools%2C%20but%20says%20that%20claiming%20%26quot%3BI've%20tried%20it%26quot%3B%20isn't%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20someone%20comes%20in%20with%20a%20vibe-coded%20app%2C%20Ritchards%20asks%20questions%20like%3A%20%26quot%3BWhy%20this%3F%20Why%20did%20you%20build%20this%3F%20What%20problem%20is%20it%20solving%3F%20Why%20are%20you%20excited%20about%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20able%20to%20utilize%20the%20best%20tools%20available%20to%20make%20your%20ideas%20real%20is%20amazing%2C%20but%20the%20foundational%20idea%20has%20to%20be%20substantive%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnap-director-product-design-ideas-degrees-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773307141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b1ab294d65ec517529d616%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnap-director-product-design-ideas-degrees-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Imani%20Ritchards%2C%20Snap's%20director%20of%20product%20design%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20looks%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Bopenness%20to%20take%20creative%20risks%26quot%3B%20while%20hiring.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchandonnet%40insider.com%20(Henry%20Chandonnet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnap-director-product-design-ideas-degrees-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20how%20far%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20could%20drop%20before%20the%20bull%20rally%20resumes%2C%20according%20to%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20CIO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222971%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trader%20at%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20viewing%20charts%20on%20a%20computer%20monitor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b190ee4d65ec517529d2c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221486%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETIMOTHY%20A.%20CLARY%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20could%20drop%20as%20much%20as%207%25%20in%20the%20next%20month%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bank's%20CIO%20said%20he%20sees%20short-term%20downside%20before%20the%20index%20can%20resume%20its%20bull%20rally.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStock%20corrections%20typically%20don't%20end%20unless%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%26quot%3B%20companies%20on%20the%20market%20get%20hit%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-rebound-signal-us-iran-war-oil-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estock%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20down%20year%20to%20date%2C%20but%20it%20might%20have%20to%20fall%20even%20further%20before%20it%20can%20resume%20its%20bull%20rally%2C%20a%20top%20Wall%20Street%20strategist%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMike%20Wilson%2C%20the%20CIO%20and%20chief%20US%20equity%20strategist%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20said%20the%20bank%20believed%20stocks%20were%20headed%20for%20more%20pain%2C%20tumbling%20as%20much%20as%207%25%20before%20the%20sell-off%20ends%20early%20next%20quarter.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20stocks%20have%20already%20taken%20a%20hit%20from%20the%20US-Iran%20war%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-oil-prices-iran-war-jpmorgan-morgan-stanley-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emarket%20corrections%3C%2Fa%3E%20typically%20don't%20end%20until%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%26quot%3B%20companies%20and%20%26quot%3Bhighest%20quality%26quot%3B%20indexes%20on%20the%20market%20see%20significant%20damage%2C%20he%20said%2C%20a%20condition%20that%20hasn't%20been%20met%20yet%20with%20the%20market's%20latest%20dip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20much%20of%20the%20damage%20has%20likely%20been%20done%20to%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20parts%20of%20the%20equity%20market%2C%20the%20index%20remains%20vulnerable%20to%20another%205%25-7%25%20downside%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20while%20crowded%20stocks%20could%20see%20double%20digit%20declines%20before%20a%20final%20low%20appears%20next%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said%2C%20speaking%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20bank's%20%26quot%3BThoughts%20on%20the%20Market%26quot%3B%20podcast%20this%20week.%3C%2F