0layoffs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%20speaks%20during%20a%20BlackRock%20conference%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b1d3c84d65ec517529dcca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20admitted%20that%20his%20industry%20is%20on%20the%20rocks%20with%20the%20American%20people.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20sees%20%26quot%3Ba%20bunch%20of%20potential%20headwinds%26quot%3B%20facing%20AI%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20not%20very%20popular%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAltman%20said%20the%20political%20headwinds%20are%20some%20of%20the%20vulnerabilities%20he%20sees%20for%20the%20US%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20going%20through%20some%20things%2C%20OpenAI%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20not%20very%20popular%20in%20the%20US%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20during%20an%20appearance%20at%20BlackRock's%20US%20Infrastructure%20Summit%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%2C%20who%20has%20previously%20spoken%20about%20how%20AI%20is%20becoming%20a%20convenient%20boogeyman%2C%20ticked%20through%20the%20list%20of%20issues%20facing%20the%20industry%20that%20could%20slow%20down%20AI%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BData%20centers%20are%20getting%20blamed%20for%20electricity%20price%20hikes.%20Almost%20every%20company%20that%20does%20layoffs%20is%20blaming%20AI%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20it%20really%20is%20about%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20this%20real%20debate%20about%20the%20relative%20power%20between%20governments%20and%20companies%20going%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20polling%20shows%20Altman%20is%20right%20to%20be%20concerned%20about%20what%20he%20said%20were%20%26quot%3Ba%20bunch%20of%20potential%20headwinds%26quot%3B%20facing%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20NBC%20News%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fpolitics-news%2Fpoll-majority-voters-say-risks-ai-outweigh-benefits-rcna262196%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoll%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2057%25%20of%20voters%20said%20the%20risks%20of%20AI%20outweigh%20the%20benefits.%20Respondents%20had%20less%20favorable%20views%20of%20AI%20than%20a%20long%20list%20of%20notable%20public%20figures%20and%20organizations%2C%20including%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20former%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris.%20A%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20survey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fscience%2F2025%2F09%2F17%2Fhow-americans-view-ai-and-its-impact-on-people-and-society%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2050%25%20of%20US%20adults%20said%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bmore%20concerned%20than%20excited%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20increased%20use%20of%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20up%2013%20percentage%20points%20since%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20and%20OpenAI%20may%20have%20exacerbated%20tensions%20by%20signing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-pentagon-deal-fallout-backlash-anthropic-altman-amodei-trump-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erushed%20deal%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20%3C%2Fa%3Eafter%20the%20Defense%20Department%20moved%20to%20effectively%20blacklist%20rival%20Anthropic.%20Altman%20alluded%20to%20the%20tension%20when%20talking%20about%20the%20debate%20concerning%20%26quot%3Brelative%20power.%26quot%3B%20He%20has%20said%20that%20while%20AI%20companies%20play%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20ensuring%20the%20proper%20use%20of%20their%20technology%2C%20governments%20ultimately%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20depend%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20headwinds%20are%20one%20vulnerability%20the%20US%20faces%20in%20the%20AI%20race%2C%20Alman%20said.%20He%20said%20the%20US%20leads%20the%20global%20AI%20race%20over%20China%2C%20but%20victory%20is%20far%20from%20assured.%20The%20OpenAI%20CEO%20said%20the%20US%20still%20needs%20to%20navigate%20issues%20with%20the%20global%20supply%20chain%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20AI%20adoption%20moves%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20don't%20move%20as%20quickly%20as%20other%20countries%20on%20economic%20adoption%20of%20this%2C%20then%20I%20think%20we%20will%20lose%20the%20advantage%20that%20we%20have%20from%20being%20the%20economic%20powerhouse%20that%20we%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20is%20about%20how%20quickly%20companies%20adopt%20it.%20This%20is%20about%20how%20quickly%20our%20scientists%20adopt%20this%2C%20how%20quickly%20our%20government%20adopts%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20US%20moves%20quickly%20enough%2C%20Altman%20said%20AI%20will%20offer%20an%20almost%20unprecedented%20chance%20to%20change%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20is%20a%20once%20in%20many%20generation%20opportunity%20to%20really%20improve%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Breally%20rewrite%20some%20of%20the%20rules%20of%20society%20that%20aren't%20working%20in%20light%20of%20this%20new%20incredible%20wealth%20fountain%20we%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ai-popularity-us-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773306541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b1d3e5a96e437d6eb82a9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ai-popularity-us-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recent%20polling%20shows%20the%20American%20people%20are%20souring%20on%20OpenAI%20CEO%20