0a%20resurgence%2C%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D36391e69b5e84b9fb79bc8143cf1e3680ac15d1a1087890aa2291ae2b66c04ab%26postID%3D69af335e7b9cac572eb98ed7%26postSlug%3Dwhen-the-bnp-paribas-open-was-less-fancy-and-crowded-2026-3%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.espn.com%252Ftennis%252Fstory%252F_%252Fid%252F47964882%252Ftennis-participation-us-rose-high-273-million-2025%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecord%20number%20of%20enthusiasts%3C%2Fa%3E%20playing%20the%20sport%2C%20according%20to%20the%20USTA.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20US%20Open%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usopen.org%2Fen_US%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-09-15%2F2025_us_open_celebrates_competition_milestones_and_shatters_fan_records.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrew%20more%20than%20a%20million%20fans%20to%20New%20York%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20blending%20intense%20competition%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-street-style-us-open-photos-what-to-wear-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecelebrity%20sightings%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20branded%20cocktails%2C%20and%20sky-high%20ticket%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20tournaments%20like%20the%20BNP%20Paribas%20Open%20are%20borrowing%20that%20playbook%2C%20betting%20that%20as%20interest%20in%20the%20sport%20grows%20beyond%20its%20traditional%20fan%20base%2C%20more%20spectators%20will%20pay%20up%20for%20a%20luxury%2C%20branded%20tennis%20event%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20longer%20lines%20and%20massive%20crowds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20huge%20tennis%20fan%2C%20I%20have%20mixed%20feelings%20about%20how%20much%20the%20tournament%20has%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20it's%20great%20to%20see%20this%20event%20thriving%2C%20after%20it%20struggled%20so%20much%20financially%20that%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Farchives%2Fla-xpm-2010-mar-08-la-sp-tennis-larry-ellison-20100309-story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%20decamped%20to%20China%20or%20the%20Middle%20East%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202010.%20Instead%2C%20Oracle%20founder%20Larry%20Ellison%2C%20then%20the%20fourth-richest%20man%20in%20the%20world%2C%20stepped%20in%20to%20save%20the%20day%2C%20with%20Tennis%20magazine%20calling%20him%20%26quot%3Bthe%20white%20knight%20of%20American%20tennis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sat%20down%20with%20Ellison%20in%202011%20after%20his%20big%20purchase%2C%20and%20he%20told%20me%20he%20considered%20it%20the%20best%20tournament%20money%20could%20buy%20(since%20Wimbledon%20will%20never%20be%20for%20sale).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20be%20happier%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2011%2F03%2F18%2F134646327%2FOracle-CEO-Ellison-Saves-PNP-Paribas-Tennis-Tournament%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEllison%20told%20me.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20a%20wonderful%20asset.%20And%20I%20love%20tennis.%20I%20play%20tennis%20five%20days%20a%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.desertsun.com%2Fstory%2Fsports%2Ftennis%2Fbnp%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2Flarry-ellisons-influence-bnp-paribas-open-goes-beyond-his-checkbook%2F2986768002%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEllison%20invested%20more%20than%20%24130%20million%20in%20the%20facilities%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20building%20an%208%2C000-seat%20Stadium%20Two%20with%20a%20swanky%20Nobu%20to%20replace%20a%20rinky-dink%20grandstand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20I%20enjoy%20indulging%20in%20Yellowtail%20Jalapeno%2C%20I%20miss%20the%20days%20when%20anyone%20with%20a%20grounds%20pass%20could%20access%20Stadium%20Two.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20tournament%20changed%20that%20policy.%20Only%20people%20who%20specifically%20bought%20tickets%20for%20Stadium%20Two%2C%20which%20could%20cost%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20for%20the%20lower%20bowl%2C%20were%20allowed.%20Many%20seats%20remained%20empty%20at%20night%20as%20ticketholders%20grew%20tired%20of%20the%20desert%20sun%20and%20headed%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20crowd%20shot%20basically%20shows%20how%20bad%20a%20decision%20it%20was%20to%20no%20longer%20let%20groundpass%20holders%20onto%20Stadium%202.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThis%20comes%20on%20a%20day%20where%20they're%20expecting%20to%20break%20attendence%20records%2C%20outer%20courts%20have%20been%20packed%20and%20meanwhile%20S2%20is%20empty%2C%20not%20fair%20on%20Svitolina%2FSiegemund%20either%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4mPW7DjGmY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F4mPW7DjGmY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Tennis%20Updates%20(%40TennisUpdates26)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTennisUpdates26%2Fstatus%2F2030532241722372329%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%208%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a791a94-0aff-4f1b-bf98-7a3c83fabf88%5C%22%3ELines%20everywhere%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20record%20504%2C268%20fans%20attended%20last%20year's%20tournament%2C%20a%20number%20organizers%20expect%20to%20be%20exceeded%20this%20year.%2058%2C828%20fans%20passed%20through%20the%20gates%20last%20Friday%2C%20setting%20a%20new%20one-day%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225232%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20crowds%20at%20the%20BNP%20Paribas%20Open%20on%20Friday%2C%20March%206th%2C%202026.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69afb58382b35e2c04dd66c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222616%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20crowds%20at%20the%20BNP%20Paribas%20Open%20on%20Friday%2C%20March%206th%2C%202026.%3Cp%3EBen%20Bergman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWalking%20around%20the%20grounds%20has%20been%20a%20test%20of%20patience%2C%20with%20long%20lines%20for%20parking%2C%20food%2C%20and%20getting%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20longest%20lines%20over%20the%20weekend%20were%20not%20even%20for%20a%20match.%20When%20I%20walked%20by%20a%20Lululemon-sponsored%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3De27e4d8d7560e199676ac4d98e71fe97c01ea17901fb52fbbdcf3e9e71ac575f%26postID%3D69af335e7b9cac572eb98ed7%26postSlug%3Dwhen-the-bnp-paribas-open-was-less-fancy-and-crowded-2026-3%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fshop.lululemon.com%252Fstores%252Fus%252Findian-wells%252Fbnp-paribas-pop-up-event%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBNP%20Paribas%20Open%20Pop%20Up%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20was%20mobbed%2C%20with%20some%20fans%20complaining%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Flululemon%2Fcomments%2F1rpjwex%2Flululemon_popup_at_bnp_paribas_indian_wells_open%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaiting%20two%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Flululemon%2Fcomments%2F1rpjwex%2Flululemon_popup_at_bnp_paribas_indian_wells_open%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20hours%20only%20to%20find%20the%20store%20sold%20out%20of%20many%20items.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224218%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20line%20to%20get%20into%20the%20BNP%20Paribas%20Open%20Pop%20Up%20-%20Lululemon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69afb56dccda166eed3d0f4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222109%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20line%20to%20get%20into%20the%20BNP%20Paribas%20Open%20Pop%20Up%20-%20Lululemon%3Cp%3EBen%20Bergman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20curious%20to%20try%20the%20Drop%20Shot%2C%20BNP%20Paribas'%20new%2C%20made-for-Instagram%20pineapple-flavored%20tequila%20cocktail%2C%20which%20it%20hopes%20will%20be%20as%20popular%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-open-tennis-honey-deuce-cocktail-review-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20Open's%20Honey%20Deuce.%3C%2Fa%3E%20But%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20waiting%20in%20another%20line%20or%20paying%20%2427%20for%20a%20drink.%20I%20asked%20some%20fans%20for%20their%20review%2C%20and%20they%20said%20they%20were%20not%20impressed%20by%20the%20taste%20but%20were%20pleased%20with%20the%20souvenir%20cup%20they%20could%20take%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224511%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Drop%20Shot%20is%20a%20new%20cocktail%20at%20the%20BNP%20Paribas%20Open%2C%20available%20for%20%2427%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69afb517441e48aec3a1c996%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222256%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Drop%20Shot%20is%20a%20new%20cocktail%20at%20the%20BNP%20Paribas%20Open%2C%20available%20for%20%2427.%3Cp%3EBen%20Bergman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20fair%2C%20I%20had%20similar%20experiences%20with%20endless%20lines%20attending%20the%20US%20Open%20and%20the%20Championships%20at%20Wimbledon%20in%20recent%20years.%20However%2C%20the%20appeal%20of%20Indian%20Wells%20has%20always%20been%20that%20it%20is%20a%20hidden%20gem%20in%20the%20desert%2C%20where%20you%20can%20run%20into%20a%20star%20player%20walking%20to%20the%20gym%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Flosangelestennisgroup%2Fposts%2F4417663458522384%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20the%20grocery%20store.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20will%20never%20forget%20seeing%20Roger%20Federer%20or%20Rafael%20Nadal%20compete%20on%20outer%20courts%20in%20doubles%20in%202014.%20I%20even%20got%20to%20eat%20in%20the%20players'%20dining%20room%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20media%20and%20once%20found%20myself%20in%20line%20behind%20Novak%20Djokovic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20physical%20demands%20and%20prize%20money%20at%20stake%20in%20today's%20singles%20game%2C%20you%20would%20never%20see%20Carlos%20Alcaraz%20or%20Jannik%20Sinner%20playing%20doubles%2C%20and%20I%20shudder%20to%20think%20how%20long%20the%20line%20would%20be%20if%20they%20appeared%20on%20a%20smaller%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b71c2683-2d74-4611-86cb-632cd233bea8%5C%22%3EStill%20'Tennis%20Paradise%3F'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20year's%20tournament%2C%20there%20is%20ubiquitous%20signage%20reminding%20us%20we%20are%20in%20%26quot%3BTennis%20Paradise%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20brilliant%20slogan%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20Philippe%20Dore%20came%20up%20with%20in%202016%2C%20as%20he%20was%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20for%20a%20post-Federer%2FNadal%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20those%20GOATS%20were%20not%20going%20to%20be%20here%20forever%2C%20so%20we%20wanted%20to%20build%20an%20experience%20regardless%20of%20what%20happens%20on%20the%20competition%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20Dore%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20people%20to%20come%2C%20whoever's%20playing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hard%20not%20to%20agree%20that%20I%20was%20in%20Tennis%20Paradise%20as%20the%20sun%20set%20on%20Friday.%20The%20desert%20sky%20was%20turning%20brilliant%20shades%20of%20red%20while%20I%20sat%20a%20few%20rows%20behind%20Denis%20Shapovalov%20as%20he%20grinded%20out%20a%20three-set%20win%20against%20Tomas%20Martin%20Etcheverry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sun%20sets%20at%20the%20BNP%20Paribas%20Open%20on%20Friday%2C%20March%206%2C%202026.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69afb67a82b35e2c04dd66c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20sun%20sets%20at%20the%20BNP%20Paribas%20Open%20on%20Friday%2C%20March%206%2C%202026.%3Cp%3EBen%20Bergman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20its%20new%20limitations%2C%20I%20would%20argue%20the%20grounds%20pass%2C%20which%20costs%20around%20%2460%2C%20is%20still%20the%20best%20deal%20in%20sports.%20If%20you%20really%20want%20to%20get%20up%20close%20to%20Alcaraz%20and%20Sinner%2C%20it's%20a%20thrill%20to%20watch%20them%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20the%20parking%20is%20still%20free.%20As%20I%20was%20walking%20to%20my%20car%20in%20the%20expansive%20grass%20overflow%20lot%2C%20I%20heard%20a%20woman%20say%20to%20her%20friend%3A%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20it%20was%20too%20crowded%2C%20but%20I'd%20rather%20focus%20on%20the%20stuff%20I%20enjoyed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20agree%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-the-bnp-paribas-open-was-less-fancy-and-crowded-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773306001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69af3846441e48aec3a1c5cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-the-bnp-paribas-open-was-less-fancy-and-crowded-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20tennis%20fan%2C%20I%20have%20mixed%20feelings%20about%20how%20much%20the%20BNP%20Paribas%20Open%20has%20changed.%20It's%20become%20more%20crowded%20and%20expensive%2C%20with%20more%20luxury.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bbergman%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Bergman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-the-bnp-paribas-open-was-less-fancy-and-crowded-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indore%20Petrol%20Pump%20Worker%20Killed%20As%20Car%20Driver%20Drags%20Him%20After%20Refusing%20Payment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22A%20petrol%20pump%20worker%20in%20Indore%20was%20killed%20when%20a%20car%20driver%2C%20who%20refused%20to%20pay%20for%20fuel%2C%20allegedly%20grabbed%20his%20hand%2C%20rolled%20up%20the%20window%2C%20and%20dragged%20him%20for%2