.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496799%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESangeeta%20employs%20innovative%20teaching%20methods%2C%20such%20as%20incorporating%20songs%20and%20interactive%20activities%20to%20make%20learning%20enjoyable.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConventional%20lesson%20plans%20fell%20flat.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20children%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20just%20sit%20and%20listen%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20brightened%20up%20when%20I%20told%20stories%2C%20sang%20songs%2C%20or%20played%20games%20with%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20began%20using%20folk%20tales%2C%20riddles%2C%20and%20interactive%20activities%20to%20make%20learning%20enjoyable.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20children%20started%20participating%20eagerly.%20They%20even%20role-played%20as%20teachers%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20police%20officers.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20classroom%20filled%20with%20laughter%20and%20energy.%20When%20the%20children%20laugh%20and%20play%2C%20they%20learn%20without%20even%20realising%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sangeeta%2C%20these%20moments%20are%20priceless.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20child%20tells%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20want%20to%20be%20a%20teacher%20like%20you%2C%E2%80%99%20my%20heart%20swells%20with%20pride.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBalancing%20two%20worlds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%