3Cp%3EParents%20might%20worry%20about%20the%20cost%20of%20microgreens%20and%20millets%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%2C%20trendy%20foods%20are%20often%20expensive%20(think%20avocados).%20But%20100%20gm%20of%20fresh%20microgreens%20straight%20from%20farms%20costs%20only%20Rs%20125%20to%20Rs%20135.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETackling%20the%20parent%20dilemma%3A%20Fussiness%2C%20time%20and%20trends%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20knowing%20the%20benefits%20and%20actually%20getting%20children%20to%20eat%20them%20are%20two%20very%20different%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CParents%20often%20tell%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98My%20child%20rejects%20everything%20except%20pasta%20and%20biscuits%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sandhya.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20trick%20is%20persistence%20and%20creativity.%20If%20a%20millet%20pancake%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%20one%20day%2C%20try%20millet%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20next%20%E2%80%94%20or%20millet%20cookies%2C%20chocolates%2C%20even%20burgers%20with%20millet%20patties.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20give%20up%20after%20one%20rejection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20adds%20her%20practical%20hacks%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20your%20child%20loves%20pasta%2C%20swap%20the%20base%20for%20millet%20pasta%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20available%20now.%20Or%20make%20the%20sauce%20more%20nutrient-rich%20by%20blending%20in%20spinach%2C%20pumpkin%2C%20or%20microgreens.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20always%20have%20to%20reinvent%20meals%2C%20just%20upgrade%20them.%20Take%20the%20foods%20they%20already%20like%20and%20make%20small%20changes.%20For%20example%2C%20add%20a%20pinch%20of%20spirulina%20to%20pancakes%2C%20make%20a%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20%3C%2Fem%3Echocolate%20popsicle%20or%20smoothie%2C%20or%20mix%20a%20spoon%20of%20amaranth%20seeds%20into%20rice.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20same%20colour%2C%20so%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20even%20notice%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20experts%20agree%20that%20a%20fun%20presentation%20matters.%20A%20spinach%20%3Cem%3Edosa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecomes%20a%20%E2%80%98Hulk%20dosa%E2%80%99.%20An%20%3Cem%3Eidli%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20eyes%20transforms%20into%20a%20bunny.%20Bento%20boxes%20%E2%80%94%20those%20colourful%2C%20compartmentalised%20lunch%20kits%20trending%20on%20Instagram%20%E2%80%94%20can%20also%20help%20make%20food%20visually%20exciting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDLALf0oSNdH%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDLALf0oSNdH%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDLALf0oSNdH%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Sanchita%20Mahtani%20%2F%20Baby%20%26amp%3B%20Toddler%20Nutrition%20Consultant%20(%40sanchitadaswani)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20slipped%20millet%20cookies%20with%20cocoa%20powder%20into%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20tiffin%2C%20I%20thought%20he%E2%80%99d%20trade%20them%20away.%20Instead%2C%20he%20came%20home%20asking%20if%20I%20could%20pack%20more%20the%20next%20day.%20It%E2%80%99s%20become%20his%20go-to%20snack%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ritu%20Sharma%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%20I%E2%80%99ve%20slowly%20started%20experimenting%20with%20other%20changes.%20A%20sprinkle%20of%20home-grown%20microgreens%20on%20%3Cem%3Edal%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Erotis%3C%2Fem%3E%20seemed%20like%20nothing%20at%20first%2C%20but%20over%20time%20he%20began%20noticing%20the%20extra%20crunch.%20These%20days%2C%20he%20even%20reminds%20me%20if%20I%20forget%20to%20add%20them.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20little%20victories%20like%20this%20that%20make%20me%20feel%20reassured%20that%20he%E2%80%99s%20getting%20the%20right%20nutrition%20without%20the%20mealtime%20battles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20working%20parents%2C%20time%20is%20a%20real%20hurdle.%20But%20Sandhya%20reassures%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20now%20brands%20offering%20ready-to-make%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336832%2Fias-officer-sushant-gaurav-transforms-gumla-district-of-jharkhand-with-ragi-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillet%20pancake%20mixes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20flours.%20Just%20add%20milk%20and%20cook.%20But%20always%20check%20the%20labels.%20Choose%20products%20with%20minimal%20preservatives%20and%20zero%20palm%20oil.%20And%20above%20all%2C%20pre-plan.%20Weekly%20meal%20prep%20makes%20life%20easier.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20not%20packaged%20foods%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20experts%20are%20cautious%20about%20heavily%20marketed%20%E2%80%9Cnutrition%20drinks%E2%80%9D%20and%20packaged%20baby%20foods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20nutritionist%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20recommend%20packaged%20milk-based%20food%20regularly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sandhya%20says%20firmly.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20be%20used%20occasionally%2C%20but%20a%20simple%20homemade%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20porridge%20takes%20just%20five%20minutes%20and%20is%20far%20healthier.%20Parents%20underestimate%20how%20easy%20traditional%20options%20can%20be.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20agrees%2C%20warning%20against%20%E2%80%9Chealth%20bars%E2%80%9D%20and%20gummies%20with%20hidden%20sugars.%20%E2%80%9CCheck%20the%20labels.%20Less%20than%20four%20grams%20of%20added%20sugar%2C%20at%20least%20four%20grams%20of%20protein%2C%20and%20no%20strange%20codes%20like%20E422%20or%20INS%20numbers%20%E2%80%94%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20checklist.%20Once%20parents%20learn%20to%20read%20labels%2C%20half%20the%20battle%20is%20won.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESigns%20that%20the%20nutrition%20plan%20is%20working%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20children%20eat%20better%2C%20the%20results%20go%20beyond%20physical%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201368px)%20100vw%2C%201368px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221368%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202019%2C%20the%20Government%20successfully%20lobbied%20for%20the%20United%20Nations%20to%20declare%202023%20as%20the%20International%20Year%20of%20Millets.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177.jpg%201368w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177-300x168.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177-768x431.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177-1200x674.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-447397%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20Government%20successfully%20lobbied%20for%20the%20United%20Nations%20to%20declare%202023%20as%20the%20International%20Year%20of%20Millets.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Flovely-view-millet-stallks-sorghum-plant-2519520043%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20fussy%20eaters%20transform%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sandhya.%20%E2%80%9COne%20five-year-old%20patient%20refused%20almost%20everything.%20By%20slowly%20introducing%20millet%20pancakes%2C%20chocolate-flavoured%20dry%20fruit%20laddoos%2C%20and%20involving%20him%20in%20cooking%2C%20we%20turned%20things%20around.%20Within%20months%2C%20he%20began%20asking%20his%20mother%20for%20the%20same%20dishes.%20His%20mood%20improved%2C%20and%20he%20became%20more%20energetic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20has%20observed%20similar%20changes%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20noticed%20improvements%20in%20focus%20and%20sleep%20patterns.%20When%20parents%20swap%20sugar-loaded%20evening%20snacks%20with%20millet%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20fruit%20smoothies%2C%20kids%20are%20calmer%20at%20bedtime%20and%20more%20alert%20in%20school.%20The%20difference%20is%20visible%20within%20weeks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGovernment%E2%80%99s%20push%20on%20the%20millet%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20isn%E2%80%99t%20leaving%20this%20revival%20only%20to%20parents.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20Government%20successfully%20lobbied%20for%20the%20United%20Nations%20to%20declare%202023%20as%20the%20International%20Year%20of%20Millets.%20The%20idea%3A%20fight%20malnutrition%20globally%20while%20supporting%20climate-resilient%20crops%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMid-Day%20meals%20in%20anganwadis%3A%20States%20like%20Karnataka%20and%20Odisha%20now%20serve%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20malt%2C%20bajra%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20jowar%20%3Cem%3Eupma%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFarmer%20support%3A%20Incentives%20for%20millet%20cultivation%20and%20processing%20encourage%20rural%20economies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAwareness%20drives%3A%20Millet%20festivals%2C%20recipe%20competitions%2C%20and%20celebrity%20endorsements%20are%20changing%20perceptions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20a%20global%20conference%20hosted%20sessions%20on%20key%20millet-related%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20including%20promotion%20and%20awareness%20among%20producers%2C%20consumers%2C%20and%20other%20stakeholders%3B%20value%20chain%20development%3B%20health%20and%20nutrition%3B%20market%20linkages%3B%20and%20research%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeyond%20nutrition%3A%20Building%20food%20relationships%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20both%20experts%20agree%3A%20food%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20nutrients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20often%20forget%20the%20relationship%20children%20have%20with%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sanchita.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20grow%20microgreens%20or%20help%20stir%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20batter%2C%20they%20value%20food%20differently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhya%20echoes%20this%2C%20drawing%20from%20Western%20practices%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20countries%2C%20children%20are%20encouraged%20to%20join%20in%20kitchens.%20Let%20them%20knead%20dough%2C%20cut%20veggies%2C%20or%20make%20pancake%20shapes.%20Even%20if%20the%20kitchen%20gets%20messy%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20more%20likely%20to%20eat%20the%20food%20they%20helped%20make.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPlanting%20seeds%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildhood%20is%20fleeting%2C%20but%20its%20foundations%20last%20a%20lifetime.%20By%20the%20age%20of%20five%2C%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20brain%20is%20already%2090%25%20developed.%20The%20foods%20parents%20offer%20in%20these%20early%20years%20%E2%80%94%20say%20millet%20%3Cem%3Edosas%20%3C%2Fem%3Einstead%20of%20instant%20noodles%2C%20microgreen%20salads%20instead%20of%20fries%20%E2%80%94%20quietly%20shape%20not%20just%20health%2C%20but%20focus%2C%20mood%2C%20and%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Microgreens%20in%20food%20grade%20trays%20are%20grown%20in%20controlled%20environment.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-